<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>nạṣyf ạlyạzjy</author>
<title>yạ bny ạlậb ạlsmạwy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā banī ạlậbi ạlsãmāwī̃̊
 ratĩlūạ waq̊ta ạlsãfar̊
 sabĩḥūạ ạl̊fādī ạl̊muʿazĩy
 wāl̊ḥabība ạl̊mun̊taẓar̊

[V2]
 2- biạkẖ̊tiṭāfiⁿ tar̊taqūna
 maʿ̊ jamīʿi ạl̊mū̊̉minīn̊
 ại̹nãhu fī suḥ̊bi maj̊diⁿ
 yal̊taqīkum̊ ʿan̊ yaqīn̊

[V3]
 3- yā qaṭīʿa ạlrãbĩ halĩl̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ naṣībuka yasūʿ̊
 walaka ạl̊maj̊du muʿaduⁿ̃
 fī dẖuray̱ til̊ka ạlrũbūʿ̊

[V4]
 4- hab̊ lanā yā rabũ nas̊ʿay̱
 biạlrãjāʾi mam̊lūyỉyn̊
 ạản̊ta ạl̊qāyỉdu wāl̊mur̊sẖid̊
 nat̊baʿan̊ka fariḥīn̊</lyrics>
</song>